Package ReadData

A package containing all classes and interfaces for reading data from the source and all related exceptions
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FormatReader
    An interface describing methods for reading and processing various source data formats
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TextReader
    Implementation of the FormatReader interface, for reading text files of the format specified in the terms of reference
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    WrongFormatException
    An exception occurs if the data format differs from the expected one
